long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
VFI YouTube Channel Monetization Checker

Find out if a YouTube channel is monetized or not, Push to Production in just one click, by using our monetization checker. Also, quickly access an history of the latest channels you checked and the result.

How to use? Just go on a YouTube channel or YouTube video, and the extension will tell you if the channel you are visiting is monetized or not.

The results are 100% accurate.

This extension works only on YouTube.
